text: Yeemeneeh meqe taamoomi Abbaasite marah tu-gactek, toysa Yalli ken taamoomih galtoota dudda-luk keenih Aceeleeh isi muxxok keenih osse-le, isi Nafsi fayya heeh kaxxa mariinite marah tu-gactek, toysa Yalli ken Qansarissa digaalah ken digaale- le, usun Yallak kalah Awlaytu mageyaanaay cateynay Yallih digaalak ken cata mageyan
